@startuml
state Arrived as "User Arrives"
state InsertedCard as "Card Inserted"
state CheckPin as "PIN Checked"
state IncorrectPin as "Incorrect PIN"
state InvalidCard as "Invalid Card"
state SecurityHold as "Security Hold"
state CancelledOperation as "Cancelled Operation"
state OptionsAvailable as "Options Available"
state ProcessRequest as "Process Request"

Arrived --> InsertedCard: user arrives
InsertedCard --> CheckPin: card inserted
CheckPin --> IncorrectPin: incorrect PIN
IncorrectPin --> IncorrectPin_again: allow try again
IncorrectPin_again --> CheckPin: check again
CheckPin --> OptionsAvailable: correct PIN
OptionsAvailable --> ProcessRequest: user chooses option
ProcessRequest --> [*]: process selected request
CancelledOperation --> ReturnCard: user cancels operation
ReturnCard --> Arrived: return card to user
InvalidCard --> SecurityHold: card is invalid or too many incorrect attempts
SecurityHold --> [*]: keep card for security
@enduml
